<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Kaia Gerber and Jacob Elordi are in separable after going public with their romance earlier this week.</p>

<p>The couple enjoyed another date in New York together on Wednesday where Elordi revealed his zany taste in clothes wearing a pair of jeans emblazoned with colorful graphic design.</p>

<p>The duo sat outside as they dined together with pals and chatted into the evening, looking content and happy for the world to know about their blossoming relationship.  </p>

<p>Inseparable: Kaia Gerber and Jacob Elordi enjoyed another date in New York City on Wednesday</p>

<p>The 19-year-old Vogue supermodel wore a pretty peach slip dress and lace-up boots for the outing while showing off her pink-tinged locks.</p>

